T02D2415:34a-1: nanhya brta tra ya mu kha a'a ga ma n'a ma /
T02D2415:34a-3: g-yung drung 'khyil pa gsum gyi zhal gdams kyi nyams len zhes bya ba /
T02D2415:34b-0: yum rnal @34b 'byor ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2415:34b-1: bla ma'i zhal gdams thob byas nas //
T02D2415:34b-2: g-yung drung gsum gyi gdams pa ni //
T02D2415:34b-3: stong nyid don ni rtogs pa'i phyir /
T02D2415:34b-4: kam ka me kha la bshad bya //
T02D2415:34b-5: rang gi lus ni khong stong la //
T02D2415:34b-6: spyi bor brtsams nas lte ba'i bar //
T02D2415:34b-7: rtsa gsum ser dang dkar dmar ro //
T02D2415:34b-8: de rnams nang ni khong stong ste //
T02D2415:34b-9: g-yas kyi rtsa la khab rtse tshad //
T02D2415:34b-10: rang bzhin bsal ba bsam par bya //
T02D2415:34b-11: g-yon par zla ba'i thig le ste //
T02D2415:34b-12: dbus kyi rtsa ni khong stong ngo //
T02D2415:34b-13: de la sems gtad phyi nang stong //
T02D2415:34b-14: shes pa rgod na g-yas g-yon gyi //
T02D2415:34b-15: thig le gnyis la sems gtad la //
T02D2415:34b-16: de nas dbu bcad dh'u tr'i'i steng //
T02D2415:34b-18: me yi mdog can rnam bsam bya //
T02D2415:34b-19: g-yung drung 'khyil pa'i zur bzhi la //
T02D2415:34b-20: aom dang a'a:dang h'um dang phat //
T02D2415:34b-21: g-yas phyogs ra sa'i steng du ni //
T02D2415:34b-22: aa las zla ba'i g-yung drung 'khyil //
T02D2415:34b-23: byang chub sems kyi chu rlung bkag //
T02D2415:34b-24: g-yon pa la na'i steng du ni //
T02D2415:34b-25: aom las g-yung drung 'khyil ba dmar //
T02D2415:34b-26: bsams pas me yi rlung 'gags so //
T02D2415:34b-27: de nas rlung gi 'khor lo nas //
T02D2415:34b-28: rlung ni langs te mgrin par sles //
T02D2415:34b-29: dbus su bde gshegs rlung rgyu bas //
T02D2415:34b-30: sor ni bcu gnyis rtsa 'thon nas //
T02D2415:34b-31: g-yas g-yon chu rlung me rlung ni //
T02D2415:34b-32: nyi zla'i rtsa nas 'byung byas nas //
T02D2415:34b-33: lha mo gnyis dag zhal du rngub //
T02D2415:34b-34: slar yang gnyis kyis phu byas pas //
T02D2415:34b-35: rtsa dag gnyis kyi rtsa bug brtol //
T02D2415:34b-36: rnam par rgyu ste g-yung drung 'phog / dbus kyi sems bskor byas nas su //
T02D2415:34b-37: gnyis ni g-yas skor g-yon skor ro //
T02D2415:34b-38: slar yang rlung gis phu byas nas //
T02D2415:34b-39: g-yung drung gnyis la thim byas nas //
T02D2415:34b-40: dbus kyi 'khyil pa thim par bsam //
T02D2415:34b-41: ye shes me sbar rang lus ni //
T02D2415:34b-42: mgrin pa'i gnas nas rkang mthil bar //
T02D2415:34b-43: rim gyis zhu ste chos dbyings su //
T02D2415:34b-44: mnyam nyid thig ler sems gtad do //
T02D2415:34b-45: brtags pas ma grub dngos med yin //
T02D2415:34b-46: dmigs pa'i mtshan nyid thams cad bral //
T02D2415:34b-47: de ltar ma bsgoms ci byas kyang //
T02D2415:34b-49: thig le de las blangs byas nas //
T02D2415:34b-50: bdag nyid dbu bcad yum du bskyed //
T02D2415:34b-51: de nas lte bar hrim yig bsam //
T02D2415:35a-2: hri ni thig le gsum du zhu //
T02D2415:35a-3: ai ni rlung gi thig le ste //
T02D2415:35a-4: ha ste byang chub thig le'o //
T02D2415:35a-5: rakta'i thig le ram yig ste //
T02D2415:35a-6: mdor na rim par sngo dkar dmar //
T02D2415:35a-7: ma shar rlung gis gyen la 'dod //
T02D2415:35a-8: dbu bcad rtsa sbubs rgyu na ni //
T02D2415:35a-9: steng du sor bzhi 'thon par bsam //
T02D2415:35a-10: g-yon pa g-yon skor g-yas pa g-yas //
T02D2415:35a-11: dbus kyi thig le 'bar zhing thim //
T02D2415:35a-12: lha mo gnyis kyis phus btab pas //
T02D2415:35a-13: g-yas g-yon theg le dbus la thim //
T02D2415:35a-14: de nyid mar la rngub byas pas //
T02D2415:35a-15: snying ga'i h'um la thim par bsam //
T02D2415:35a-16: de ni gsal la dri ma med //
T02D2415:35a-17: gnyis med thig le rang rig ste //
T02D2415:35a-18: bde dang sdug bsngal thams cad bral //
T02D2415:35a-19: 'khor ba snang ba rang rig stong //
T02D2415:35a-20: kye ho rnal 'byor bsgoms nas ni //
T02D2415:35a-21: gnyis med ye shes thob par 'gyur //
